Class ColorPaletteCell

All Implemented Interfaces:
Cell<String>, HasSelectionHandlers<String>, HasHandlers
public class ColorPaletteCell
extends AbstractEditableCell<String,String>
implements HasSelectionHandlers<String>

A Cell Widget representing a palette of colors.

Note: the word Cell in the class name refers to a GWT cell, not an individual cell in a color palette.
